snippet.title: The Sacred Pools Sega Saturn
snippet.description:
I found this while archiving my old vhs tapes.
Originally rerecorded from an e3 1995-96? tape.
near the end was a promo real for each company at the time Nintendo, Sega  a Sony. This was cut from Sega SegaSoft part
